            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Right, so if a redraw happens somewhere, the re-emit still happens and there's no way to detect this is a resend right?\nSome kind of flag in the `msg_show` or msg id to know it has already been processed would be great.\n\nCurrently I just discard msg_show events if they're the same as the last one, but this also means if you echo the same message twice, Noice will only show it once.",
